metadata.name: NetEmpire No-Reveal
metadata.description:
NetEmpire is the Planet IX corporation for commerce and domination. By holding the NetEmpire Genesis NFT, you will continuously receive airdrops from the corporation.

Genesis NFTs have a value as an NFT that can be traded and sold. But also as an asset that will generate further NFTs, MetaShares, and other in-game assets for the holder, forever and from the entire Planet IX ecosystem.

There will never be another mint of the NetEmpire Genesis.
